Grab this in my bio! (Read below) 

This is for anyone that’s interested in Vocal Production and wants a free reverb / delay send mixer template with all routing and stock plugins  included! 

When you sign up for the template, you’ll also be added to the Vocal Hacking Early Bird list if you’re not in it yet… 

This is great because if you’re interested in vocal production with FL Studio, I’m opening my online course THIS SUNDAY for the early bird list only. Then Monday for the general public! 

Can’t wait to see you in the vocal hacking community! 

Ya Get Me

#recordvocals #mixingvocals #vocals #vocalproduction #recordingstudio #Flstudio #flstudio20 #producertips #808 #flstudiotips #producer #prod #musicproducer #musicproduction #makingbeats #beatmaker #producers #flgang

I am SUPER excited that registration for my online course "Vocal Hacking" will open in a few days.

So,

If you’ve signed up for the early-bird waitlist you’re lucky because your chances of getting a spot are a lot higher.

Again I’ll only be taking a small handful of new students and working with them side by side to master their vocal production. 

If you’re not signed up to the early-bird waitlist, you still have a little bit of time to sign up in my bio. 

But on a more important note: 

Here's how to make sure you get a spot….

1. Make sure you're on the early-bird waiting list 
2. Open your inbox on Sunday, 12th of September at 1PM EST
3. Refresh your inbox until you receive the early-bird registration email
4. Open the email, click on the link and secure your spot asap

If you follow these exact instructions you should have no problems getting into the class. But really make sure you sign up on Sunday, at 1PM EST.

It might be a good idea to set up a reminder on your phone so you don't miss the deadline. There's going to be a rush to the registration page on Sunday, so make sure you're one of the first to visit the signup page and lock in your spot.

I hope you can make it into the class.
